    <chapter num="5">
        <verse num="1">
            <content> </content>
            <content> Mpoopoo w’ani nkyer&#603; &#596;panin, na mmom tu no fo s&#603; agya, mmerante&#603; s&#603; anuanom, </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="2">
            <content>mmaa mpanimfo&#596; s&#603; &#603;nanom, mmabaa s&#603; nua mmaanom w&#596; ahote&#603; nyinaa mu.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="3">
            <content> </content>
            <content> Di mmaa akunafo&#596; a w&#596;y&#603; akunafo&#596; ampa no ni. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="4">
            <content>Na s&#603; okunafo&#596; bi w&#596; mma anaa mmanana a, w&#596;nsua onyamesom pa w&#596;n fie mu kane, ntua w&#596;n awofo&#596; ka; &#603;firi s&#603; yei na &#603;y&#603; na &#603;s&#596; Nyankop&#596;n ani. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="5">
            <content> Na de&#603; &#596;y&#603; okunafo&#596; ampa, na aka ne nko no, &#596;de n’ani to Nyankop&#596;n so, na &#596;kura nkotosr&#603; ne mpaeb&#596; mu anadwo ne awia. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="6">
            <content>Na de&#603; &#596;b&#596; ahohwie no de&#603;, &#596;y&#603; teaseawuo. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="7">
            <content>Yeinom ho na hy&#603; w&#596;n, na w&#596;annya w&#596;n ho as&#603;m bi anka. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="8">
            <content>Na s&#603; obi nhw&#603; &#596;no ara ne nnipa, ne titire no ne fiefo&#596; a, wapa gyidie, na &#596;y&#603; onipa b&#596;ne sene de&#603; &#596;nnye nnie.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="9">
            <content>W&#596;mmfa okunafo&#596; a &#596;nnya nnii mfirinhyia aduosia nhy&#603; mu, na mmom w&#596;mfa de&#603; waware kunu baako, </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="10">
            <content> de&#603; w&#596;di no ne ne nnwuma pa ho adanse&#603;: S&#603; way&#603;ne mma, s&#603; way&#603; ah&#596;hoy&#603;, s&#603; wahohoro ahotefo&#596; nan ho, s&#603; waboa w&#596;n a w&#596;n ho ahia w&#596;n, s&#603; wadi adwuma pa nyinaa akyi.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="11">
            <content>Na akunafo&#596; a w&#596;nnyinii&#603; de&#603;, mfa w&#596;n; na s&#603; Kristo ho fono w&#596;n a, na w&#596;p&#603; s&#603; w&#596;ware&#603;, </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="12">
            <content>na w&#596;nya afobuo s&#603; w&#596;apa kane gyidie no. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="13">
            <content>Na emu ara nso na w&#596;y&#603; aniha sua afie mu kyinkyini, na &#603;ny&#603; aniha nko na w&#596;y&#603;, na w&#596;y&#603; anokurokuro ne ter&#603;ter&#603; nso keka ns&#603;m a &#603;ns&#603;.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="14">
            <content> </content>
            <content> Enti mep&#603; s&#603; akunafo&#596; a w&#596;nnyinii&#603; no ware wo mma di efie so&#596;, na w&#596;amma &#596;tamfo&#596; ho kwan s&#603; &#596;nni at&#603;m; </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="15">
            <content>&#603;firi s&#603; ebinom amane ak&#596;di Satan akyiri dada. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="16">
            <content>S&#603; &#596;baa gyidini</content>
            <note_ref>1</note_ref>
            <content> bi w&#596; akunafo&#596; a, &#596;nhw&#603; w&#596;n, na &#596;mmma no nny&#603; asafo no adesoa, na asafo no ahw&#603; w&#596;n a w&#596;y&#603; akunafo&#596; ampa no.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="17">
            <content> </content>
            <content> Mpanimfo&#596; a w&#596;hw&#603; asafo no so yie no, w&#596;mfa anidie mm&#596;ho nni w&#596;n, ne titire no, w&#596;n a w&#596;y&#603; as&#603;nka ne nkyer&#603;kyer&#603; ho adwuma. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="18">
            <content> Na atwer&#603; no se: Nantwie a &#596;pore ayuo no, ma no nni bi, ne: Odwumay&#603;ni akatua s&#603; no. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="19">
            <content> Ntie asafo mu panin ho kwaadub&#596;, gye adansefo&#596; baanu anaa baasa anomu. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="20">
            <content> W&#596;n a w&#596;y&#603; b&#596;ne no, yi w&#596;n at&#603;n w&#596;n nyinaa anim, na w&#596;n a aka no nso asuro.</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="21">
            <content>Mehy&#603; wo Onyankop&#596;n ne Awurade Kristo Yesu ne ab&#596;fo&#596; a w&#596;ayi w&#596;n no anim, s&#603; hw&#603; yeinom yie, na woampere ho ammu at&#603;n, nso woany&#603; biribiara nyiyimu so. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="22">
            <content> Mfa wo nsa ngu obi so nt&#603;m, nanso mfa wo ho mfra ebinom b&#596;ne mu. Sie wo ho kronn. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="23">
            <content>Nnom nsuo nko bio, na wo yafunu ne wo mmer&#603; a wotaa y&#603; no nti, nom bobesa kakraa bi!</content>
            <content> </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="24">
            <content>Nnipa binom b&#596;ne da adi pefee de w&#596;n k&#596; atemmuo mu, na ebinom de&#603; nso di w&#596;n akyi. </content>
        </verse>
        <verse num="25">
            <content>Saa ara na nnwuma pa nso da adi pefee, na s&#603; any&#603; saa mpo a, &#603;nhunta.</content>
        </verse>
